extends helpers/layout

block head
	title welcome

block content

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width=width)
		td(valign='top', width=width, colspan='2')
			p(style='width: 500px; margin: 30px 0; padding: 0 30px 0 50px; font-size:13px; line-height: 21px;')
				| We hope your first experiences with Aviate Beta have been great! We’re so happy to have you onboard. We built Aviate to simplify your phone and surface information at the moment it’s useful and I'm writing today to share some of the features that we think deliver on this vision. 

	+separator( 3 )


	tr(style=backgroundColor, width=width)
		td(valign='top', width=width, colspan='2')
			p(style='width: 500px; margin: 30px 0 0; padding: 0 30px 0 50px; font-size:14px; line-height: 27px;')
				| <strong>I hope you try a few things that make Aviate great:</strong>

			p(style='width: 500px; margin: 0 0 0; padding: 0 30px 0 50px; font-size:13px; line-height: 21px;')
				| - Update your homescreen with your favorite photo and widgets</br>
				| - Make sure we included all your favorite apps on your homescreen</br>
				| - Set your alarm and put your phone in Do Not Disturb mode tonight from the Home Space</br>
				| - Check out the tips on what to order next time you go to a restaurant</br>

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width=width)
		td(valign='top', width=width, colspan='2')
			p(style='width: 500px; margin: 20px 0 0; padding: 0 30px 0 50px; font-size:14px; line-height: 27px;')
				| <strong>More information:</strong>
			p(style='width: 500px; margin:0 0 0; padding: 0 30px 0 50px; font-size:13px; line-height: 21px;')
				| We also put together a <strong><a href="http://bit.ly/H10Gzv" title="Aviate FAQ">FAQ</a></strong> with some of the most common questions we've been asked.

	+signature( "Thanks for trying Aviate,", 'Paul Montoy-Wilson, Co-Founder ', true )

	+separator( 3 )

	//- Post Script
